<PageLayout>
  <main class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl">
    <div class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Cookie Policy</h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl mb-12 text-gray-600">
        SalesTag uses cookies to improve your experience and keep your account secure. This policy explains what cookies are, how we use them, and how you can control them.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device to remember your preferences and improve functionality. SalesTag uses cookies responsibly to enhance your experience while respecting your privacy choices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">What Are Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Cookies are tiny data files that help websites remember who you are and what you've done. They're essential for modern web applications and enable features like staying logged in, remembering your preferences, and providing personalized experiences.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We use essential cookies for login and security, functional cookies to remember your preferences, and analytics cookies to understand how SalesTag is used. We don't use advertising cookies or tracking cookies for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">How to Control Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          You can manage cookies through your browser settings or our cookie preferences center. You can accept all cookies, reject non-essential cookies, or customize your preferences. Note that blocking essential cookies may limit SalesTag's functionality.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 scroll-mt-24">Third-Party Cookies</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We may use third-party services like analytics providers that set their own cookies. These services help us understand how SalesTag is used and improve our platform. You can opt out of these third-party cookies through your browser or privacy settings.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</PageLayout> 